{"tid":1952236,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣科技大臣唐鳳拍片教乾蒸口罩 提醒順時鐘跑8分鐘[影]","createTime":"2020-03-31T13:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T14:53:07.000Z","uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e1595c06b2af1f927e2852175878bd5be11dda","tid":1952236,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:06:42.000Z","msg":"台灣科技大臣唐鳳拍片教乾蒸口罩 提醒順時鐘跑8分鐘[影]<br />\n最新更新：2020/03/31 19:12<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgFyjXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgFyjXY.jpg&h=c9952370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫情使口罩成為重要防疫物資，行政院政務委員唐鳳31日在推特貼出乾蒸口罩教學影片。（<a href=\"http://圖取自twitter.com/audreyt）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AAtwitter.com%2Faudreyt%EF%BC%89&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhoMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=17ae46f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自twitter.com/audreyt）</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者顧荃台北31日電）武漢肺炎疫情使口罩成為重要防疫物資，行政院政務委員唐鳳今天在推特發影片，進行乾蒸口罩的消毒教學，並拿一個時鐘計時，提醒「時鐘要順著跑8分鐘」。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情升溫，國內口罩供不應求，中山醫學大學職安系副教授賴全裕經過檢測證實，「電鍋乾蒸法」可使口罩復活，但只能重複乾蒸使用5次。<br />\n<br />\n唐鳳今天在推特貼出乾蒸口罩教學影片，她在片中模仿美食節目說：「今天要教大家，怎麼樣做一道簡單的乾蒸口罩。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/audreyt/status/1244780164564701184?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faudreyt%2Fstatus%2F1244780164564701184%3Fs%3D20&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhoMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=1a55551b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faudreyt%2Fstatus%2F1244780164564701184%3Fs%3D20&h=54f8363a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/audreyt/status/1244780164564701184?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n唐鳳表示，要準備一個電鍋、一片用過的口罩，和一個時鐘；把口罩平放在電鍋中，「原汁原味不加水」。蓋上鍋蓋、按下電源之後，「讓時鐘順著跑8分鐘」。之後把鍋蓋打開，稍微放涼之後，就完成消毒可重複使用的口罩。<br />\n<br />\n唐鳳的影片以中文說明，加上英文字幕，目前已有超過9萬人次觀看，推文並加上「TaiwanCanHelp」（台灣可以幫忙）。（編輯：謝佳珍）1090331<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202003310364.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202003310364.aspx&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhoMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=9b667402\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202003310364.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"ee8961214f9d3101091b3a50d89fc5059d04263a","tid":1952236,"uid":337341,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:09:35.000Z","msg":"香港代表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3v2qp3mF6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP3v2qp3mF6E&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhoMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=32941932\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3v2qp3mF6E</a>"},{"pid":"6016c7acdd774a01fcaabebb673134be94e3dc66","tid":1952236,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:10:14.000Z","msg":"台灣一星期三片喎，重玩這些野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9452dd2c309b4d6e846bc0d9776b293adcfb0d10","tid":1952236,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6016c7acdd774a01fcaabebb673134be94e3dc66","tid":1952236,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:10:14.000Z","msg":"台灣一星期三片喎，重玩這些野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:11:01.000Z","msg":"給海外台僑看的"},{"pid":"6c20d7446495df0348ad614955191835ed2c02ba","tid":1952236,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee8961214f9d3101091b3a50d89fc5059d04263a","tid":1952236,"uid":337341,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:09:35.000Z","msg":"香港代表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3v2qp3mF6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP3v2qp3mF6E&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhoMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=32941932\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3v2qp3mF6E</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:12:24.000Z","msg":